---
// Hero section component for AI Agent Infographic Showcase calling NotebookLM
---

<section class="w-full flex flex-col items-center text-center mx-auto py-12 md:py-24 px-4">
  
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-8 text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider">
    <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-primary/20">AI Agent Skill</span>
    <span class="text-zinc-500">+</span>
    <span class="bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-indigo-500/20">infographic-creator</span>
  </div>

  <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-[7.5rem] font-black leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-foreground mb-8">
    Agentic <br/> 
    <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-secondary to-cta">
      Infographic
    </span> <br/>
    Intelligence
  </h1>

  <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-foreground/70 max-w-3xl mb-12 leading-relaxed">
    A massive, searchable database of domain contexts, visual styles, and structural layouts. 
    Build beautiful, highly-customized infographics instantly using the AI Agent Skill, calling different providers (NotebookLM, Google AI Studio, Antigravity, or OpenAI) to compile high-fidelity graphics.
  </p>

  <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-4 mb-20 w-full sm:w-auto">
    <a href="#how-it-works" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-primary hover:bg-sky-400 text-white font-bold rounded-full transition-all duration-300 text-lg shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 hover:shadow-primary/50 hover:-translate-y-1">
      How it Works
    </a>
    <a href="#gallery" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-zinc-800 hover:bg-zinc-700 text-white font-bold rounded-full transition-all duration-300 text-lg border-2 border-zinc-700 hover:border-zinc-500">
      View Showcase Gallery
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Agent Chat Session UI Mockup -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-4xl bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-800/80 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6 mb-20 text-left relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background glow shapes -->
    <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-48 h-48 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 w-48 h-48 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

    {/* Header */}
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse"></div>
        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-200 tracking-tight">Active Session: Infographic Agent</span>
      </div>
      <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 text-slate-400 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 select-none">
        AI Agent Skill
      </span>
    </div>

    {/* Chat Stream */}
    <div class="space-y-6">
      
      {/* Bubble 1: User Prompt */}
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 justify-end">
        <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none p-4 max-w-xl text-right">
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-200 leading-relaxed font-medium">
            "Please create a 5-stage treatment flowchart for Type 2 Diabetes using professional blues and calming greens."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-zinc-400 text-xs shrink-0 select-none">
          USER
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Skill Activation Indicator */}
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 px-4 py-1.5 bg-purple-950/40 border border-purple-500/30 text-purple-400 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest animate-pulse">
          <span class="text-purple-400">⚡</span>
          <span>Triggering Skill: infographic-creator</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Bubble 2: AI Agent Output */}
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary/20 border border-primary/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-primary text-xs shrink-0 select-none">
          AI
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-950 border border-slate-850 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none p-5 max-w-2xl flex-1 space-y-4">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-400 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-400">
              <span class="font-bold">✔</span>
              <span>Audit intent & map structure: Process Flowchart (HC-001)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-purple-400">
              <span class="font-bold">✔</span>
              <span>Applying visual guidelines: Calming & Clean Clinical Guidelines</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sky-400">
              <span class="font-bold">✔</span>
              <span>Generating HSL color palette swatches: #007BFF (primary), #28A745 (positive)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-zinc-400">
              <span class="animate-pulse text-amber-500">⚙</span>
              <span class="animate-pulse">Rasterizing visual SVG canvas zones into high-resolution pixels...</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          {/* Preview Image */}
          <div class="mt-4 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative group bg-slate-900/60 p-2">
            <img 
              src="/infographics/hc_001_treatment_protocol.png" 
              alt="Treatment Protocol" 
              class="w-full h-auto max-h-[350px] object-contain rounded-xl"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-[2px] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl">
              <a href="#gallery" class="px-6 py-2.5 bg-white hover:bg-slate-100 text-slate-900 font-bold rounded-full text-xs shadow-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                Explore in Gallery Below
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Statistics Row -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 md:gap-16 w-full py-8 border-y border-zinc-800/80">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-foreground mb-2">5</span>
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground/60 uppercase tracking-widest">Domains</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-foreground mb-2">12</span>
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground/60 uppercase tracking-widest">Structures</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-foreground mb-2">10+</span>
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground/60 uppercase tracking-widest">Visual Styles</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-foreground mb-2">68</span>
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground/60 uppercase tracking-widest">Active Blueprints</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
